attrs.script:
#!/bin/bash
set -ex

sudo mkdir -p /opt/gitlab
sudo yum install -y lvm2 --quiet
sudo pvcreate /dev/sd{b,c,d}
sudo vgcreate gitlab /dev/sd{b,c,d}
sleep 3
sudo lvcreate -l 100%VG -n gitlab_lvm gitlab
sudo mkfs.xfs /dev/gitlab/gitlab_lvm

echo -e "/dev/gitlab/gitlab_lvm \t /opt/gitlab \t xfs \t defaults \t 0 0" | sudo tee -a /etc/fstab
sudo mount -a

#!/bin/bash
set -ex
GITLAB_DNS_NAME=@@{GITLAB_DNS_NAME}@@

if [[ "${GITLAB_DNS_NAME}x" == "x" ]]; then 
  echo "Variable 'GITLAB_DNS_NAME' is unset; defaulting to 'gitlab.example.com'"
fi

sudo yum install -y curl policycoreutils-python openssh-server postfix 

sudo systemctl start postfix
sudo systemctl enable postfix
sudo systemctl status postfix

curl https://packages.gitlab.com/install/repositories/gitlab/gitlab-ce/script.rpm.sh | sudo bash

sudo yum install -y gitlab-ce
if [[ "${GITLAB_DNS_NAME}x" != "x" ]]; then 
  sudo sed -i "s#external_url 'http://gitlab.example.com'#external_url 'http://${GITLAB_DNS_NAME}'#" /etc/gitlab/gitlab.rb
fi
sudo gitlab-ctl reconfigure

action_list.description: System action for creating an application
action_list.name: action_create

action_list.description: System action for uninstalling an application
action_list.name: action_uninstall

sudo systemctl enable postfix
sudo systemctl status postfix

curl https://packages.gitlab.com/install/repositories/gitlab/gitlab-ce/script.rpm.sh | sudo bash

sudo yum install -y gitlab-ce
if [[ "${GITLAB_DNS_NAME}x" != "x" ]]; then 
  sudo sed -i "s#external_url 'http://gitlab.example.com'#external_url 'http://${GITLAB_DNS_NAME}'#" /etc/gitlab/gitlab.rb
fi
sudo gitlab-ctl reconfigure
